Package edu.sjsu.cs151.spaceinvader.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Alien
    Alien object that extends Sprite class.
    Barrier
    Barrier object that extends Sprite class.
    Board
    Board (Model) stores all information about the current state of the game and handles collision detection and player movement.
    Bomb
    Bomb class extends the Sprite class and contains the methods and properties to set, move and destroy the player object.
    GameTemplate
    Implementation of TEMPLATE design pattern which involves an abstract class that exposes defined ways/templates to execute its methods.
    Player
    Player class extends the Sprite class and contains the properties for the player vehicle and methods to read key presses for movement and firing.
    RandomSingleton
    Implementation of SINGLETON design pattern which involves a single class which is responsible in creating only one object of itself.
    Shot
    Shot class extends the Sprite class and contains the methods and properties to set, move and destroy the Alien object.
    Sprite
    Sprite class contains the necessary variables and methods to get/set positions of objects, set visibility, and get/set the image itself.
